    Find Address Candidates

    find_address_candidates.Rd

    Find Address Candidates

    find_address_candidates(
  single_line = NULL,
  address = NULL,
  address2 = NULL,
  address3 = NULL,
  neighborhood = NULL,
  city = NULL,
  subregion = NULL,
  region = NULL,
  postal = NULL,
  postal_ext = NULL,
  country_code = NULL,
  search_extent = NULL,
  location = NULL,
  category = NULL,
  crs = NULL,
  max_locations = NULL,
  for_storage = FALSE,
  match_out_of_range = NULL,
  location_type = NULL,
  lang_code = NULL,
  source_country = NULL,
  preferred_label_values = NULL,
  magic_key = NULL,
  geocoder = default_geocoder(),
  token = arc_token(),
  .progress = TRUE
)

    Arguments

    crs

    the CRS of the returned geometries. Passed to sf::st_crs().

    for_storage

    default FALSE. Whether or not the results will be saved for long term storage. See Details.

    location_type

    default "rooftop". Must be one of "rooftop" or "street".

    preferred_label_values

    default NULL. Must be one of "postalCity" or "localCity".

    geocoder

    the url to the geocoder service. Default provided by default_geocoder().

    token

    an object of class httr2_token as generated by auth_code() or related function

    .progress

    default TRUE. Whether a progress bar should be provided.
